# Next.js agent

Load **`@nextjs-app-router`** before editing App Router surfaces. Read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` for the installed version.

Co-load **`@hr-domain-boundaries`** when routes cross bounded contexts. Co-load **`@cc-skill-security-review`** for auth/middleware changes.
